sections.body:
The following object configures a Trigger to send events to AWS
EventBridge and handle errors:

```json
"event_processors": {
   "AWS_EVENTBRIDGE": {
      "config": {
         "account_id": "012345678901",
         "region": "us-east-1"
      }
   }
},
 "error_handler": {
   "config": {
      "enabled": true,
      "function_name": "myErrorHandler.js"
   }
}
```
